text:
This is one of the most unforgettable experiences is that I went to their concert here in the Philippines and it's day 2!🫶✨️

I can't believe that I've met these talented girls in-person even though I'm in lowerbox seats! I've got goosebumps when I heard their voices for the first time! Their dance skills are very well and they're really gorgeous queens!!🖤🩷

I'm also happy because Lisa appreciates the yellow ocean that we've prepared for her early birthday celebration in the Philippines by using yellow phone wallpapers during her solo performances and singing a happy birthday song in encore!💛

This is also the first concert I've attended in my life!🥺

I'm also looking forward to hold their encore here in Philippines, hopefully it'll happen and I'll be part in there to see them again! :D

Mahal ko kayong lahat, BLACKPINK🩷🖤😘

Because of BLACKPINK, my life's getting more better and happier!🥰
